{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_09_02",
  "title": "奥山すみれ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-02",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "オーディションから、三日で、もう共演者と最初の\n顔合わせか……なかなかタイトなスケジュールだな",
      "startTime": 4.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "オーディション、合格出来て良かったです！\nこれも{user}さんのおかげです",
      "startTime": 12.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "全部すみれの努力の結果だ\nすみれがどんなに頑張ったか、瑠依達から聞いてるよ",
      "startTime": 17.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "移動中どころか、お風呂にまで台本を持ち込んで\n読み込んでいたそうじゃないか",
      "startTime": 24.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "は、恥ずかしいっちゃ～！！\n瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんのバカ～！",
      "startTime": 29.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "……こほん、でもそれだけじゃありません",
      "startTime": 31.8333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが練習に付き合ってくれた\nおかげです。本当にありがとうございます！",
      "startTime": 39.1666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺なんかの演技が役に立ったなら、何よりだよ\n……そろそろ始まるな。すみれ、頑張って",
      "startTime": 47.4666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　行ってきます、{user}さん",
      "startTime": 51.2000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロダクション所属、奥山すみれです！\n演技のお仕事は久しぶりですが――",
      "startTime": 60.5999968211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "みなさんの足を引っ張らないように頑張ります\nご指導ご鞭撻、よろしくお願いします！",
      "startTime": 66.5333301544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（この映画の共演者は、舞台出身の実力者が多い）\n（この中じゃすみれが一番若い……ファイトだ、すみれ）",
      "startTime": 74.1333301544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "ご主人様、お茶をお淹れしました……どうぞ",
      "startTime": 79.8333342235,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7233.3328247,
          "startTime": 87.0666670482
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ……",
      "startTime": 88.6333204906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。初回にしては上出来だったんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 90.3999871572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんにはそう見えましたか……",
      "startTime": 94.4999871572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "演技のことは、正直俺にはよく分からないけど……\nでも、監督には一度も注意はされなかっただろ？",
      "startTime": 102.9333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかして、注意しないんじゃなくて\n出来なかったんじゃないでしょうか……",
      "startTime": 111.966672643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ……？\n……分かった。気分転換に、どこか寄って帰ろうか",
      "startTime": 117.8666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "はい。すみません……",
      "startTime": 122.5333159129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 126.9499871571
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 126.9499871571
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの話だけど、監督がすみれに注意出来ないって\nどういうことだ？",
      "startTime": 132.2333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "休憩中に、聞こえちゃったんです\n他の共演者さん達の話し声が……",
      "startTime": 137.7333382924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 141.3999932606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "私は実力で選ばれたんじゃない\n映画の客寄せ要員だって……",
      "startTime": 144.8000049591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "なっ！　そんなこと……",
      "startTime": 148.3666578928,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 150.4666558583
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "ないって……言い切れますか？\n私に役者としてブランクがあるのは本当です",
      "startTime": 155.5000029247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "そんな私がオーディションに合格したのは\n実力じゃなくて……",
      "startTime": 163.4333382924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 165.5666558583
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "元人気子役で、TRINITYAiLEの\n奥山すみれだから……",
      "startTime": 169.5000049591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 171.933322525
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "そんな風に考えたら……体がうまく動かせなくなって",
      "startTime": 171.933322525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "私はただ出ていればいいだけの存在だから\n監督は演技指導をしないのかなって……",
      "startTime": 183.1333382924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 187.3999881744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……俺はオーディションの結果には関与していない\nだから、すみれが合格になった理由は分からない",
      "startTime": 190.6666706085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "だから、すみれの言う通りなのかもしれない",
      "startTime": 194.4999769847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 198.2666487377
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "そう……ですよね",
      "startTime": 198.2666487377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 202.0666487377
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "だけど、それがどうした？",
      "startTime": 202.0666487377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "芸能界が一筋縄ではいかない、綺麗なだけの世界\nじゃないことは、すみれだって知ってるだろう？",
      "startTime": 208.6999876659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 211.9666487377
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
